<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/nav%3Aside/interwikiFrame.html?category=log-of-anomalous-items-cn&pagename=log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00260" class="html-block-iframe scpnet-interwiki-frame" name="interwikiFrame"></iframe></p>
